manifests.contents:
[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "gizo"
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
edition = "2021"
required-features = []

[package]
name = "gizo"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"

[dependencies]
hyper = "1.6.0"
image = "0.25.5"
lazy_static = "1.5.0"
regex = "1.11.1"
serde_json = "1.0.138"
thiserror = "2.0.11"
urlencoding = "2.1.3"

[dependencies.axum]
version = "0.8.1"
features = ["macros"]

[dependencies.reqwest]
version = "0.12.12"
features = ["json", "rustls-tls"]
default-features = false

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.217"
features = ["derive"]

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.43.0"
features = ["full"]

[dependencies.tower]
version = "0.5.2"
features = ["limit"]

[dependencies.tower-http]
version = "0.6.2"
features = ["trace"]

[profile.release]
opt-level = 3
lto = true
codegen-units = 1
panic = "abort"
strip = true

[profile.release.package]
